108
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:11,880
Tourists jockey for camera position in Arches and Canyonlands to show their Instagram followers

109
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,880
they've been there.

110
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:17,200
