130
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:35,560
The social media craze of documenting experiences in the outdoors has spread beyond Instagram

131
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:36,560
and Twitter too.

132
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:40,760
